data.description: Beautiful Bissonet Plaza home .... well maintained, great area schools, shopping, local restaurants and more. Luscious Landscaped yard is wonderful for entertaining and relaxing. Enjoy being outside under covered carport, front and back porches. The home flows well with abundant natural light. The interior is in excellent condition as home has been updated and well maintained through time.  Recent Updates include:  Renovated Baths, New Roof, new wood Floors, new Gutters and more.  This beauty boasts a large open kitchen and dining area, spacious living room, and a comfort that makes this home great for any type of gathering.  Shed is powered with electrical for your outdoor work needs.  Located in the heart of Metairie. This is a must see property.
